### Which @angular/* package(s) are the source of the bug?

compiler, language-service

### Is this a regression?

No

### Description

After using optional chain operator and reading a nested property I get a false error in the template:

```
interface SomeType {
  a: {
    b: string;
  };
}

@Component(...)
class Component {
    prop?: SomeType = { a: { b: "Me" } };
}

<p>{{ prop?.a.b }}</p>
              ^ error TS2532: Object is possibly 'undefined'.
```

